{"tid":2181594,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"醫管局員工陣線籲杯葛普及社區檢測計劃","createTime":"2020-08-30T16:39:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-30T16:49:01.000Z","uid":79563,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"99d02a911676c180cf1a78b4f0f03d1cf53ad316","tid":2181594,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T16:39:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1546854-20200830.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1546854-20200830.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=lPj0fEAhrWGYZLLoA4iNoJNY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=2992db22\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1546854-20200830.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=04cd9d6c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1546854-20200830.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n醫管局員工陣線聯同部分民主派人士開記者會，呼籲杯葛後日展開的「普及社區檢測計劃」。工會質疑，全民檢測原意是要找出隱形病人，但沒有居家令和封關配合，病毒依然會傳播。<br />\n<br />\n醫管局員工陣線參考美國文獻，指出病人接觸到病毒的首日，假陰性機率達到100%，要到發病第3日假陰性機率才降至20%，之後數日假陰性的機率又會回升，因此認為病人檢測一次，不可作準。<br />\n<br />\n工會質疑政府推行全民檢測有政治原因，又說如果政府肯及早封關，並配合科學和實證為本的防疫策略，相信現在香港已可以作息如常。"},{"pid":"11535043b708d9ac79ca117a33373ad56dc0f1d9","tid":2181594,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T16:46:20.000Z","msg":"支持醫護"},{"pid":"b89500cb4c8c78670b845a88301fb5ae8966b5c0","tid":2181594,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T16:49:01.000Z","msg":"放心 藍絲都唔驗"}]}